caption: Table 1: Symbol meaning

caption: Table 2: Hyperparameters of experiment
description: This table lists the hyperparameters used in the experiments described in the paper.  It includes parameters for the overall training process (total timesteps, number of environments, etc.), the optimizer, batch size, learning rate, and the architecture specifics for different neural network components (RNN layers, QMIX and Qatten modules, knowledge integration).
